	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Path integration</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
		<div id="contentSub"></div>
		
		
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This article is about animal navigation. For the mathematical technique, see <a href="/wiki/Line_integral" title="Line integral">Line integral</a>.</div>
<p><b>Path integration</b> is the method thought to be used by animals for <a href="/wiki/Dead_reckoning" title="Dead reckoning">dead reckoning</a>.
</p>
<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:332px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Path_integration_diagram.svg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/88/Path_integration_diagram.svg/330px-Path_integration_diagram.svg.png" decoding="async" width="330" height="242" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/88/Path_integration_diagram.svg/495px-Path_integration_diagram.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/88/Path_integration_diagram.svg/660px-Path_integration_diagram.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="873" data-file-height="640" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Path_integration_diagram.svg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>Path integration sums the vectors of distance and direction travelled from a start point to estimate current position start.</div></div></div>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
